name: WorldOfJZ
short_description: The WorldOfJZ Project is anew project started by Jesse that allows you to create your own world and then you can build on it. Sort-of like Minecraft or Legos.  WorldOfJZ is a game that lets you create your own worlds and just BUILD on them. You can also submit your maps to the World Of JZ website for other members of the program to view and download.This project is currently in its alpha stages but the first release is available to download. Check out the "Downloads" page to download the FIRST edition of WorldOfJZ. Development team: Created by Jesse and Tested by Lucas. Thank you!
summary: WorldOfJZ is a game where you can generate worlds and build on them!
